Package com.hp.jipp.pdl.pwg

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PackBits
    Encoder/Decoder for the PackBits algorithm described in the Wi-Fi Peer-to-Peer Services Print Technical Specification v1.1
    PwgHeader
    All elements of a PWG Raster header as described in section 4.3 of PWG-5102.4.
    PwgReader
    An InputStream that can read a class RenderableDocument from PWG-Raster input
    PwgSettings
    Provide settings for PWG-Raster output.
    PwgWriter
    An OutputStream that can write a class RenderableDocument in PWG-Raster format.
